<item rdf:about="https://medical.nikkeibp.co.jp/leaf/mem/pub/di/column/dsjpranking/202401/582819.html">
<title>感染症が猛威振るう中、ツムラ葛根湯が限定出荷</title>
<link>https://medical.nikkeibp.co.jp/leaf/mem/pub/di/column/dsjpranking/202401/582819.html</link>
